locality: Yemen: Gov. Al-Mahra. flat gravelly wadi 5 km W of Qeshn. Small flat shrubs in the gravel of a flat wadi. Flowers and fruits present. Alt.: 20 m. 24.9.1998, Leg.: P. Hein, S. A. Ghazanfar & N. Kilian PH 4893.
